            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港股恒生指數開升230點或0.9%，報25761，恒生科技指數開升56點或1.02%，報5591 ; 恒生國企數開升78點或0.88%，報9013點。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"滙豐。巴士的報記者攝\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20250305_CR_Source-web_HSBC_02.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"滙豐。巴士的報記者攝\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20250305_CR_Source-web_HSBC_02.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">滙豐。巴士的報記者攝</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">大市成交21.56億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滙控(00005)升1.84%，報116.1元 ; 阿里巴巴(09988)升1.39%，報152.7元 ; 騰訊(00700)升1.08%，報608元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">小米(01810)升1.14%，報42.66元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">寧德時代(03750)升2.95%，報523元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">紫金(02899)升3.51%報34.24元。</p>\n</div>",
